305
00:16:05,202 --> 00:16:06,753
70% survival rate.

306
00:16:06,838 --> 00:16:09,673
Died November 6, 1998,

307
00:16:09,724 --> 00:16:11,892
64 years old.

308
00:16:14,479 --> 00:16:15,879
