caused your daughter's illness
are the ones

328
00:17:31,233 --> 00:17:32,500
you shot her full of.

329
00:17:32,567 --> 00:17:34,439
I tested the drug.
This is what I did

330
00:17:34,442 --> 00:17:36,760
for a living
for ten years.

331
00:17:36,811 --> 00:17:38,311
She's your child,
not a Guinea pig.

332
00:17:38,396 --> 00:17:40,680
I tested it first.

333
00:17:40,765 --> 00:17:43,099
On myself.

334
00:17:43,167 --> 00:17:46,002
And in six months,
I didn't document

335
00:17:46,070 --> 00:17:47,570
any adverse effects.

336
00:17:47,638 --> 00:17:50,240
A trial of one
is basically irrelevant.

337
00:17:53,694 --> 00:17:56,362
Respiratory infections
are common with A-T.

338
00:17:56,447 --> 00:17:58,698
With Emily's mutation,
