408
00:22:08,532 --> 00:22:10,700
That's not gonna
be an issue.

409
00:22:10,751 --> 00:22:13,369
I'm glad at least one of us
is confident.

410
00:22:13,437 --> 00:22:14,404
<i>Not me.</i>

411
00:22:14,471 --> 00:22:16,005
I've already identified

412
00:22:16,073 --> 00:22:17,373
