to dump your body

413
00:22:17,441 --> 00:22:19,742
if this goes south.

414
00:22:19,810 --> 00:22:22,845
I've always enjoyed
Trinity Park.

415
00:22:22,913 --> 00:22:26,432
It does have a nice access
to the lake.

416
00:22:26,517 --> 00:22:29,102
<i>Muscle spasms already?</i>

417
00:22:29,186 --> 00:22:31,437
No.
It's nothing really.

418
00:22:31,522 --> 00:22:34,357
Good news.

